{"tid":1393141,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[8月5號]To所有打工仔嘅一封信","createTime":"2019-08-01T03:52:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-01T07:54:17.000Z","uid":137291,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9e57676fd15441d3ad500fd5c4456c173b4a7a56","tid":1393141,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:52:49.000Z","msg":"To所有打工仔: <br />\n    身為一個打工仔，為咗保住飯碗保住份工你可能8月5號未必夠膽出嚟罷工，因為你驚俾人秋後算賬同埋驚俾人炒，我都深深明白你地嘅感受。<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以我地更加需要多人</span></span><br />\n    點解要多啲人呀?!?因為公司總需要人力物力，如果多人一齊罷工，根本冇可能炒曬咁多人，再者，一個咁冇器量嘅老細真係值得你跟隨咩?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港死咗，錢有咩用?</span></span><br />\n    再講，如果最後香港真係死咗，你唔會後悔當時冇企出嚟咩? 就算俾你繼續返工，拎曬勤工獎嗰啲，到時香港已經死咗，俾大陸完全接管，到時完全冇言論自由冇發言權仲要做二等公民，俾你搵到幾多錢又有咩用?<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">工，可以再搵</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港，只有一個</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">打工仔，係時候企出嚟喇，8月5號約定你!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\nBy一個熱愛香港嘅人仕"},{"pid":"5e7b19cf05d0ed5fb0dbd790a765f78a8f0568d4","tid":1393141,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:53:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"08a297dfd146434bf302b3944fc424ab78fcd28f","tid":1393141,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:53:32.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25414ea3c6567f8f24ebb7c65628397ad0e7018a","tid":1393141,"uid":137291,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-01T03:54:33.000Z","msg":"之前冇出過嚟但有心嘅人宜家有機會喇<img src